edu.sjsu.cs.ghost151

Enum Board

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Board>
      • edu.sjsu.cs.ghost151.Board
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Board>

    public enum Board
extends java.lang.Enum<Board>
    Board provides the Grid for the simulation. Additionally, it will:
    • set the walls on the perimeter of the Board place an object at a given position by calling BoardObject
    • get the surroundings of a given position by calling BoardObject
    Author:
    Alben Cheung, MD Ashfaqul Islam, Shaun Guth, Jerry Phul
